com.yworks.yfiles.layout

Class DpKeyItemCollection<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.ItemCollection<T>
      • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.DpKeyItemCollection<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the items in the collection.

    public class DpKeyItemCollection<T>
extends ItemCollection<T>
    An item collection that allows to specify the data provider key the collection is registered with.

    This class supports LayoutData implementations and does not usually have to be used explicitly.
